mulahazat wangh shaw
hadha hu almakan aladhi yatimu fih tasjil mulahazat alsayid wanghi. mulahazat wangh shaw
qal kamu fi almuqadimat 'iina alhayaat eabathiatun, lakin 'iidha sa'alatni, fahi fi alwaqie 'ashbah bialfawdaa. hadha sahihun, laqad aietaqadt fi albidayat 'anani faylasuf sakhif, lakinani alan 'adrakt 'anani fi alwaqie faylasuf qumamatun. hunak maqulat tasir ealaa ma yurami, qum bitajmie jamie 'anwae alkutub mean, wasawf tatawasal mae baediha albaed watakhliq 'ashya' jadidatan. laqad dafaeat dayman ean nazariat wahsh alkhiatati, mimaa yaeni 'anah fi almujtamae alhadithi, kulu shakhs hu wahsh khiatatu. bifadl almaerifat alati aistaweabatha, walkutub alati qara'atuha, wamaqatie alfidyu alqasirat alati shahadatuha, walfanu aladhi 'ahabahu, walturuq alati safarat fiha, khalaqat afradan fridin. kayf 'aerif nafsi? ruh aljrunj alati yumathiluha kurt kubin, lidhalik qararat 'an 'asbah mmthlan lifalsafat aljurunji. eindama bada'at kitabat hadha almaqal li'awal maratan, shaeart bi'ana kamu mamsus bi, lakinani aiktushifat lahqan 'ana ladia kubin akhar. lidhalik aietaqadat 'anah sayakun min al'afdal alluju' 'iilaa falsafat alqumama (bqae alshuhumu, walsakinati). walakin wifqan liruh tasnif alqumamati, la yazal yataeayan ealayna tanzim alqumamat watasnifiha.
alhayat alyawmiat lilqumamat - fi alhayaat alsilmiati, alqumamat mawjudat fi kuli makan
fi mujtamae alyawma, tujad 'adabiaat waraq altawalit walbaramij alhawariat fi kuli makani. alnufayat al'akadimiati, huthalat alhayaati.
kalimat yangh li, ya rajulu, qumamata! lamas alqilba. 'aetaqid 'anaha tastatie aydan almusharakat fi almunaqashat hawl falsafat alqumamati.
ma aladhi sayakun shayean fi eam 2024? 'akhdh 'ashya' kabiratin, wanaql al'ashya' 'iilaa makan ma, wajamie 'anwae fatayat almarahidi. alshabab qaliqun waeatilun ean aleimla, wamae dhalik fa'iinahum yutawirun mashaeir tafihatin.
