qal ChatGPT 'iina alkitab aladhi katabtuh kan ghayr munazam wakanat 'afkari taqfizu. li'akun sadqan, satasheur binafs alshueur eindama tadhhab 'iilaa makabi alnufayati. asfa, hadhih hi simat falsafat alqumamati. hal ra'ayt ramz aljabal alqirfi? hadha hu al'adab aljabaliu alqadhira. lakina shishan kud hu fi alwaqie kud jinshan li'anah yumkinuh kasb almali. 'adab shishan hu aydan 'adab jinshan, li'anah yumkin 'an yajlib altanwir lilnaasi.
kayf taerif nafsika? muatin min lawan, dhahabt 'iilaa alkuliat fi shanghahay limudat 5 sanawat waeisht fi shikaghu limudat 5 sanawat wa'ana aydan muatin min shikaghu. laqad zurt niuyurk wa'ana min sukaan niuyurki. 'aqimt fi hiustun limudat 6 'ashhur washarakat aydan fi juz' Texas Cowboys. eazif jitar akhar musab bialhawas walaiktiaab min siatil. wafi waqt lahiq, ead 'iilaa alsiyn wataearad lisadmat thaqafiat eaksiat 'ukhraa. lidhalik 'ana 'amrikiun wamin lwan. kilahuma min 'amrika alshamaliat wa'amrika aljanubiati.
manzil sayidati aleajuz la 'aerif alsababu, lakinani kunt 'atahadath ean alsayidat aleajuz mundh 'an kunt tflaan, lakinahum fi alwaqie walidan jadi. rajul eajuz waimra'at eajuzi. manzil alsayidat aleajuz hu manzil turabiun qadim namudhajiun min 'usrat tshingh. laqad zarat maskan maw tsi tungh alsaabiq fi shawshan, wahu manzil masnue min judran turabiatin. 'iidha tama taqlisuh 6 marati, fasayabdu tqryban mithl manzil alsayidat aleajuz. tuhibu alsayidat aleajuz tarbiat aldajaji, wghalban ma tafuh rayihat baraz aldajaj min alfana'a. alsayidat aleajuz hi fi alwaqie sadiqatan tamaman. lakinah aibn shahida, wa'asbah waliduh shhydaan lilhizb alshuyueii, lakin tama alqabd ealayh fima baed wa'asbah edwaan fi hizb alkumintanghi. lidhalik laday dima' kulin min hizb alkumintangh walhizb alshuyueii. wal'amr al'akthar 'iitharatan lilghadab hu 'ana dima' alhizb alshuyueii 'aeqabaha awlaan dima' alkumintanghi. 'ana fi hayrat min 'amri aydan.
linakhudh hadhih almarat alati eudt fiha 'iilaa madrasati lihudur muhadarat 'ahad alkhubara' kamithali, wafi kuli marat kan hunak aizdiham shadidun, kunt 'arfud qabulaha waidturirt 'iilaa albad' min alsafri. rubama tuejibuni halat alwusul 'iilaa almustawaa alkamil thuma aleawdat 'iilaa alsifr maratan 'ukhraa. wahadha ma yusamaa bi'iieadat alfath. wabima 'anani khalidu, fa'iina taqdim baed alqimat aleatifiat liljumhur hu maenan wujudi. yaqul baed alnaas 'iinah mithlama hadath mae maw tsi tungh fi alsabeiniaati, fa'iina aljamie muteabun bialfiel walam yaeud bi'iimkanihim allaeb mae alrayiysi. lakin la bas fi qawl alhaqiqati. wabaed 'an mara aljamie bi'ashya' sakhifatin, 'adrakuu 'ahamiyat alqawanin wallawayihi. bimaenaa akhara, bdlaan min aintizar munqidh yunqidh alnaas min alnaar walma'i. wamin manzur akhar, qad yakun hadha almasih aydan msdran lilfawdaa. walidhalika, fa'iina karizma alqiadat alshakhsiat yajib 'an tunazam fi nihayat almataf min khilal alqawaeid wallawayihi. 'aetaqid bishakl eamin 'anani shakhs multazim bialqawaeid 'iilaa hadin ma wa'aqbal almawt ka'amr muslim bihi. rubama hadha alnawe min alraqs bial'aghlali, wa'ada' dwju dakhil qawqaeat alhalzun dimn alqawaeidi, hu alsaeadat alati 'aseaa 'iilayha fi alnihayati. 'aetaqid 'anani salbiun tmaman aydan
jamieat shanghahay ladayha aleadid min altaqalubat walmuneatafati. wafqan lilmadrasati, fa'iina altariq 'iilaa alhaqiqat mutaearji. fi kuli marat eind alqiadat 'iilaa muftaraq altariqi, kan alsikritir dingh yaqul 'iina al'ard mustadiratun, walakin eindama yasil 'iilaa siatil, kan yaqulu, lakina alturuq fi siatil munhaniatun. fi alwaqie, bighadi alnazar ean altariqat alati tatajawal biha, sawf tasil fi alnihayat 'iilaa ruma. 'ana 'uwmin bihadha bishidatin. wakama 'akad alrayiys maw fi kuli maratin, fa'iinana sawf nantasir fi nihayat almatafi.
tuufiy baed al'ashkhas ean eumr yunahiz 22 eaman, wama zal baed al'ashkhas yaemalun kamubarmijin maywuws minhum fi sinin 32 eaman. wabaed 'aqali min shahr min aindimamih 'iilaa alsharikati, qutl Yue Fei ealaa yad aleamat Bao. madha yumkinuni 'an 'afeala? 'antazir bihudu' wusul alkhati albaligh min aleumr 35 eaman. laqad tahadathat 'iilaa bayie fatayir fi altaabiq alsuflii fi maebad jinghan, waqararat baye alfatayir 'iidha lam 'atamakan min aleuthur ealaa eamal. laqad sa'alat aydan starbuks wamakdunaldiz fi mintaqat jinghan, wayabdu 'anahum ealaa aistiedad liqubuli. yabdu 'ana hunak eddan la bas bih min al'amakin alati targhab fi aistiqbali fiha.
baed qira'a "sajilat almanatiq algharbiat li'usrat tanghi", 'adrakat 'ana shwanzangh lam yakun tlmydhan 'imbratwryan 'ahdar maeah wathayiq altakhlis aljumruki, bal kan eddan qlylan min alruhban aladhin 'araduu aldhahab 'iilaa alsama' algharbiat lilhusul ealaa alkutub almuqadasati, walakina almaswuwl alrasmia lam tasmah bidhalika, lidhalik dhahab Xuanzang 'iilaa hunak min tilqa' nafsihi. yasheur alsiyniuwn dayman bialthiqat fi 'anahum bihajat 'iilaa shay' muetamad rsmyan. 'inn altulaab al'ajanib aladhin tareahum alhukumat hum dayman 'akthar fayidatan min alruhban aladhin yatimu tahribuhum bishakl khasa. walakin fi baed al'ahyan ealayk kasr alqawaeidi! yasheur alshaeb alsiyniu dayman 'ana hunak hajat 'iilaa silsilat min wathayiq altakhlis aljumrukii li'iikmal aleamaliati. fi alwaqie, la, laqad kan mujarad mash, wasafar 'iilaa aleadid min al'amakini, walshay' al'akthar ghmwdan hu 'ana shwanzangh taelam aydan lughat 'ajnabiatin, wadhahab liltanafus mae almaeabid fi alhindi, thuma ead 'iilaa watanih al'umi baed alaintiha' min almunafasati.
limadha dhahabt 'iilaa maebad jinghan li'akl alfakihat almuqadamat 'amam sakyamwny? lam yafham shangh mudir markaz alsihat aleaqliat fi shanghahay. bibasatatin, hadha hu almantiqa: bima 'ana kula shakhs yumkin 'an yusbih budha, sawa' 'asbahat budha 'um la, fal'amr matruk lika, lidhalik talama kunt taetaqid 'anak budha, fa'ant budha. 'an tusbih budha la yaetamid ealaa alkhariji, bal ealaa aldaakhil faqat. wabieibarat 'ukhraa, yumkin li'ayi shakhs 'an yakun budha. biaietibari budha, la haraj fi 'an 'arkud lilhusul ealaa alqarabin min budha. fi dhalik alyawm ra'ayt rhbanan haqiqiiyn fi almakan aladhi tama fih harq albukhur fi maebad jinghan. albudhiat alhaqiqiat hi fi alwaqie 'iilhadiatun, walzinu alhaqiqiu la yahtamu bishakl altaebira. sa'alani sayidi hal 'ant mumtan li'ana alfakihat tughadhiy jasadi? 'ajabt binaeama...wlakunani fi alwaqie dafieat 50 ywanan muqabil altadhkirati, lidha...
ghalban ma yurafiquni maw tsi tungh waswn wu wakaw kaw limushahadat albahr fi 'ahlami. taqul qasidat kaw kaw: "'anzur 'iilaa albahri". kama katab maw tsi tungh qasayida. laqad ra'awa jmyean albahr baed 'an faealuu shyyan kbyran, wara'ayt albahr aydan baed 'an faealat shyyan kbyran lilbiladi. bimujarad 'an ra'ayt tilk alsuwrata, earafat 'anah albahr alshaasie. fi alsaabiqi, kan maw tsi tungh watsaw kaw yatatalaean nahw alqarat al'amrikiat min aitijah alsiyni, baynama kunt 'atatalae nahw masqat rasi min aitijah alqarat al'amrikiati. laqad saeadathum ealaa ruyat almanazir alati lam yaruha.
la tazal alqumamat bihajat 'iilaa alfaraz.
fi alwaqiei, alquat alruwhiat jayidat jdan, khasatan eind aistikhdamiha fi musiqaa alruwka. yajib tasjil hadha alnawe min alhayawiat alghazirat walhayawiat waistikhdamuha karamz limusiqaa alruwk aljamihat waghayr almuqayadati. 'iidha aistamaet 'iilaa musiqaa alhifi mital 'akthar waeazafatha 'akthara, fasawf tuzhir 'ashya' mukhtalifat bialfiela. albahth ean alnizam fi alfawdaa. 'ana fi alwaqie 'ahibu alairtijal waistikshaf musiqaa aljaz. baed kuli shay'in, la tujad jalsatan limusiqaa aljaz mutamathilatani, wahadha hu jawhar musiqaa aljaz.
