yuqal fi nazariat alharb 'anah muqaranat bialdarar alnaajim ean tahawur alqayid muqaranatan bialdarar alnaajim ean taradudika, famin al'afdal bialtaakid 'an takun mthwran. limadha? li'anah lam yakun yatasaraf min muntalaq aljubna, bal bisabab eawaqib aljur'at ealaa altasarufi.
raqm 600 tariq wanbingh aljanubii (laqad 'aradt astikhdam hadha aleunwan lifatrat tawilatin!)
mulakhas 'uwli: baed 'an astakhdam alkalban Zhao Gou waQin Hui thamaniat eashar midaliatan dhahabiatan liaistidea' Yue Fei waYue Pengju maratan 'ukhraa, qamuu biqate ras Yue Pengju bimiqsalat ras altinin, walakin bishakl ghayr mutawaqae qam jasad Yue Fei bilasq alraas mean maratan 'ukhraa. qal Yue Fei li Zhao Gou 'iinah la bi'as, la bi'as, sa'aeud 'iilaa almanzili. wabihadhih altariqati, eudt 'iilaa almanzil ealaa maraan wamasmae min aljamie wastukhdimat hatifi almahmul lishatm tshin hui watishaw jawin ealaa Moments waZhihu waWeChat waBilibili. fi sabah alyawm altaalia, astayqaz Yue Fei, walakin qabl 'an yunazif 'asnanuh 'aw yaghsal wajhahu, qal walid zawjatih la Yue Fei, "hal turid aldhahab 'iilaa Wanping South Road li'iilqa' nazrati?" aitasal yu fay ❓ waqal 'iinah yajib ealayna 'an nadhhab wanaraa mean almarad aleaqlia wirathi bishakl eami.
'akhbar yu fay walid zawjatih 'anana sanaeish fi mustashfaa lil'amrad aleaqliat libaqiat hayaatina! baed aldukhuli, 'adrakt 'ana hadhih hi aleamat baw, alsayid baw. ma hu aljunun aladhi dafaeak 'iilayhi? 'akhbarani 'ahad alrifaq min maktab al'amn alqawmii dhat marat 'ana 'ahad zueama' 'iihdaa altawayif aldiyniat sayantahi bih al'amr fi mustashfa lil'amrad aleaqliat fi alnihayati. lan 'akun mhdhban maeka, sa'astabdil 'ahaduhuma bialakhar, wasayadkhulan mean. tariq wanbingh aljanubii hayth sataeish madaa alhayaati!
waqal fayinman fi dhalik alwaqt 'iina hadha altabib alnafsia 'aswa min altabib alsaahiri. 'aetani altibu alsiyniu ealaa al'aqali sbban lilqawl bi'ana hunak alkathir min alrutubati. rafad altabib alnafsia bibasatat 'iieta' alsabab waiktafaa bialsuwal ean aldawa'i. 'awha, man lam yaemal fi sharikat tibiyatin? hal taetaqid 'ana ealaqati mae 'iidarat alghidha' waldawa' al'amrikiat dhahabat sudan? naeud 'iilaa almushkilat maratan 'ukhraa: qal altibu algharbiu 'iinani musab bimarad eidali, lakina altiba alsiynia qal 'iinani bikhayrin. fahal yajib 'an 'astamie 'iilaa kuli dhalik wa'araa ma hi alnatayija?
alkhatu alfasil alwahid bayn almajnun waleabqarii hu ma 'iidha kan qad haqaq 'aya shay'in. tama tashkhis 'iisabat jun nash bialfasami, lakina dhalik lam yamnae jun nash min 'an yusbih 'ahad 'aezam eulama' alriyadiaati.
raqm 600 tariq wanbingh aljanubi, masqat rasi 'iilaa al'abdu. kthyran ma nati wanadhhab wanatahadath wanadhaka.
mrhban bialjamiei, 'ana yangh quh wayangh ghazi, walidi hu yangh kanghi. laqad taearaft ealaa walidi biaietibarih lsan. mataa? aintilaqan min mazharihi, famin alsahl 'an naqul 'anah wasim. -wangh buzi, 2022
qabl bideat 'ayaam dhahabat 'iilaa alfirqat wawuzieat alma' ealaa 'aeda' alfirqati, qaluu alkathir min alma'i, ya malik alma'i. qult, kayf earaft 'ana laqabi fi almadrasat althaanawiat kan "malik alma'i" [dayiratan]?
ealaa 'ayat hali, fi kuli maratin, baed 'iitharat dajat kabirat fi alqasr alsamawi, yaeud 'iilaa kawnih dhalik alqird alnitin. faqat taetad ealaa dhalika. altariq 'iilaa altaealum tawil. ealaa alraghm min 'ana halat alnnyrfana jayidatun, 'iilaa 'anaha la yumkin 'an tastamira lifatrat tawilatin. lidhalik 'aetaqid 'anah la yazal yataeayan eali tahsin nafsi.
qal kamw 'ana alsuwal alfalsafia aljidiya alwahid hu alaintihar. lidha fa'iina almawt fi hadith sayaarat 'amr sakhif hqan. wal'akthar sakhafatan hu 'an tawalad min jadid fi hadith sayaaratin. khilal hadith alsayaarat hadha, wast aldababi, shaearat 'ana rasi kan maylan tmaman, wakan ladaya shueur bialkhuruj min aljasad. walakin kanat hunak quat sihriat 'aslahat jasadi almushawah. hunak nadbat ealaa rasi litadhkiri bieadam aleawdati.
lam yatlub 'ahad min qaysar eubur alruwbikun. lam yukhbir 'ahad liunardu dafinshi 'anah yajib ealayk rasm almunaliza. yajib 'an tati jamie al'aemal aleazimat fi alwaqie min khifat alharakat alkhasat bihim.
mustaqbal eazimun. kulu al'ashya' aljayidat wal'ashya' alsayiyat hi fi alwaqie 'ashya' jayidatun. li'anak satusbih 'ant fi alnihaya
